snippet.title: Half-Life Rally Multiplayer
snippet.description: Background music starts at 1:22. This is me playing a round of Half-Life Rally. The video was made in 2004, when this mod was still pretty active and servers were full. This mod was amazing, I had a lot of fun playing it.
